This article is a presidential memorandum issued by President Barack Obama on March 16, 2012. The memorandum delegates reporting functions specified in Section 1045 of the National Defense Authorization Act for Fiscal Year 2012 and Condition 9 of the Resolution of Advice and Consent to Ratification of the New START Treaty. The President delegates these functions to the Secretaries of State, Defense, and Energy. The Secretary of Defense is also authorized and directed to publish this memorandum in the Federal Register.